modules.name: Type.Data.List
modules.comments: Type-level heterogenous list of kinds for PureScript

declarations.comments: Prepends any `Item'` to a `List'`, creating a new `List'`.
declarations.title: Cons'

declarations.comments: Performs membership testing given an `Item'` and a `List'`.
declarations.title: IsMember

declarations.comments: Internal type class that acts as an accumulator.
declarations.title: Init'

declarations.comments: Returns the last item of a `List'`.
declarations.title: Last

declarations.comments: Computes the length of a `List'` as a `Type.Data.Peano.Int`
declarations.title: Length

declarations.comments: Internal type that acts as an accumulator
declarations.title: Length'

declarations.comments: Takes an `n` amount of `Item'`s from a `List'`.
declarations.title: Take

declarations.comments: Drops an `n` amount of `Item'`s from a `List'`.
declarations.title: Drop
